    <abstract>
      <para>Snail and slug abundance were measured for a 10 year period between 1997 - 2006 at three elevations on Watershed
      1 as well as in a reference area west of Watershed 6. Watershed 1 received calcium additions as wollastonite (CaSiO3) during the 
      study period. This data set includes counts of snails and and slugs for the entire study period.</para>
    </abstract>
